@paulhayes2189¬† I love it! Absolutely love it. With aircon, infotainment and lights I think the range is more like 150 miles, but I can go a whole week to and from work on one charge. Charging at motorway services can be painfully slow, but if you're passing a Gridserve Electric Highway like the one a Braintree, Essex its soooo fast!! I went from 49% to 85% in 15 minutes. The footwell size is no issue at all, even if I'm wearing big winter boots there's plenty of room. Climate Control is a blessing in winter and very efficient at defrosting. You can pack a huge amount in it, with or without dropping the back seats.
The turning circle it small, and being a small car, you can park in some pretty small spaces.
In short, I have no regrets getting my 500e, none at all üòä

